{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"cfc5793b-0c5c-4bdc-afb9-c11032ef0781","content":"**In MAUI, `AddScoped` effectively behaves like `AddSingleton`.**\n\nIn ASP.NET Core, each HTTP request automatically creates a new DI scope, so scoped services get a fresh instance per request. MAUI has no such mechanism — the app creates **one scope for its entire lifetime**, so your `DbContext` is reused forever.\n\n### Fixes\n\n**Option 1: Use `AddTransient`**\n```csharp\nbuilder.Services.AddTransient<MyDbContext>();\n```\nA new instance is created every time it's injected.\n\n**Option 2: Create scopes manually**\n```csharp\n// Inject IServiceScopeFactory, then:\nusing var scope = scopeFactory.CreateScope();\nvar db = scope.ServiceProvider.GetRequiredService<MyDbContext>();\n```\nThis gives you explicit control over the DbContext lifetime, similar to the per-request behavior you're used to.\n\n**Option 1 is simpler** for most cases. Use Option 2 if you need a consistent DbContext across multiple services within a single operation.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"1ee200cc-c0f2-4ebc-904c-213f1891b881","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about a common pitfall when transitioning from ASP.NET Core to .NET MAUI regarding dependency injection scoping — specifically why `AddScoped` behaves differently in MAUI than in ASP.NET Core.\n\nThis is a conceptual question I can answer directly without needing to search any codebase.\n\nIn ASP.NET Core, `AddScoped` creates a new instance per HTTP request — each request gets its own scope, so a scoped DbContext is fresh for each request.\n\nIn .NET MAUI, there's no concept of an HTTP request. The DI container creates a single scope for the entire application lifetime. \n\nThis means `AddScoped` effectively acts like `AddSingleton` in MAUI — your DbContext persists across the entire app session and page navigations. To get the behavior you'd expect, I'd either switch to `AddTransient` for a fresh instance each time, or manually manage scopes using `IServiceScopeFactory`.","outputTokens":497,"requestId":"B80E:36941C:181684:1F4598:69FFDA24"},"id":"3856b70e-bc1c-4604-b07d-7d7c405a9257","timestamp":"2026-05-10T01:06:56.266Z","parentId":"39d03844-d40d-4314-83b2-27962a4b9186"}
